# Digital Workspace Automation — Intelligent File Router

Build an event-driven file routing system that watches an `Inbox/` folder, classifies files using a multi-API intelligence chain (Mistral → Grok → OpenRouter), moves them to categorized folders, and logs every action to Notion.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Folder Paths**: The user's spec targets `~/Kiza/desktop/` which may not exist. The plan uses the spec's paths exactly. If you want different paths, let me know before I proceed.

