## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests

#### [NEW] [test_workspace_engine.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/tests/test_workspace_engine.py)

Offline unit tests (no API calls, uses mocks):
- Test `setup_folders()` creates all directories
- Test `process_file()` with mocked API responses → verifies correct folder routing
- Test keyword escalation logic (Grok is only called for ML-related content)
- Test `InboxHandler.on_created` triggers `process_file`
- Test dry-run mode doesn't move files

```bash
cd /home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje && python -m pytest tests/test_workspace_engine.py -v
```

### Manual Verification

1. Run `python workspace_main.py --setup` → verify all 7 folders are created under `~/Kiza/desktop/`
2. Run `python workspace_main.py --dry-run --scan` → verify it processes files in Inbox without moving them, logs routing decisions to stdout
3. *(Optional, requires live API keys)* Drop a file into `~/Kiza/desktop/Inbox/` and verify it gets classified and moved
